<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a01"/><p id="pI01p0084a0101">
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a02"/>維大魏永熙三年歲次□□□三
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a03"/>月癸未朔五日丁<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亥</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a04"/>夫大覺遷方。託靈<note n="0084001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30585;＝像【史】</note><app n="0084001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30585;</rdg></app>以□福。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">雖</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a05"/>謝世。寄三乘以存教。自非遠鑒幽
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a06"/>源。寧能<unclear cert="low" reason="damage"><note n="0084002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30356;＝辨【史】</note><app n="0084002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30356;</rdg></app></unclear>其由。是以法義兄弟二
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a07"/>百人等。識攬玄宗。敬<note n="0084003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04572;＝崇【史】</note><app n="0084003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">崇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04572;</rdg></app><note n="0084004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30401;＝正【史】</note><app n="0084004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">正</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30401;</rdg></app>法。減<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">割</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a08"/>家財。仰為皇帝　陛下。令為七世
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a09"/>父母。營造<note n="0084005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30525;＝微【史】</note><app n="0084005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30525;</rdg></app>福。始訪石孤巖。<note n="0084006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30442;＝瑍【史】</note><app n="0084006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30442;</rdg></app>珍
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a10"/>玄豁。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">采</unclear>□妙手。敬造尊<app source="0084001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">像</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30585;</rdg></app>一區。二
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a11"/>侍菩薩。嚴姿超絕。色<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">精</unclear>琨寶。光拂
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a12"/>紫虛。暉洞皎日。崇&CI0003;於幽蹤。依
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a13"/>悕於聖容者也。緣□微因。願令亡
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a14"/>者遊神西方淨佛國土。現存同福
<lb ed="C I" n="0084a15"/>長<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">保</unclear>遐□。一切　群生。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">共</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沐</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">澤</unclear>。</p>
</div2>
